<paragraph id="5C21369B8E25FF9A908BB8D2634F6913" blockId="2.[166,1225,751,1002]" box="[219,877,751,778]" pageId="2" pageNumber="233">L o c a l i t y. Lake Berizka and the Danube delta (table 1).</paragraph>
